data.value:
Our school in 2077...
The virus that spread during the 2020s wiped out almost 80% of the population by 2030. After humans died, the virus mutated in order to survive and began to attack animals and plants as well. We are in 2077, and the few who are still alive are fighting for food and water every day.
We are soldiers of Szeged's only remaining garrison, and we are working to collect data from the machine rooms of our abandoned and infected former school.
We found out that a student at the school may have known the origin of the virus and the cure. Maybe he was the one who created it. We need to find his files on the back up servers, but in order to access the server room, we need to collect informations about the machines.
We start the research in the engine rooms, which are marked it with an X on the map. In case we were not successful, don't expect anything good in the future...
Good Luck For Us... See you soon...
